@node LICH_ "Lich"

@{b}Lich@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = A/B/UL(R)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = BBBB
Artist  = Daniel Gelon

Text(UL): You lose all life. If you gain life later in the game, instead
          draw one card from your library for each life. For each point of
          damage you suffer, you must destroy one of your cards in play.
          Creatures destroyed in this way cannot be regenerated. You lose
          if this enchantment is destroyed or if you suffer a point of
          damage without sending a card to the graveyard.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_L.guide/LICH_}

@endnode
