@node WORDO "Word of Command"

@{b}Word of Command@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = A/B/UL(R)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = BB
Artist  = Jesper Myrfors

Text(UL): You may look at opponent's hand and choose any card opponent can
          legally play using mana from his or her mana pool or lands.
          Opponent must play this card immediately; you make all decisions
          it calls for. This spell may not be countered after you have
          looked at opponent's hand.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_W.guide/WORDC}

@endnode
